{"id":313893,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/09/维权网-广东茂名多位村民因抗议政府征地封海遭/","date":"2013-09-17T09:18:01Z","modified":"2013-09-17T09:18:01Z","title":"维权网 | 广东茂名多位村民因抗议政府征地封海遭警察殴打（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></span></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员李军报道）广东省茂名市电白县建设茂名滨海新区，在电城镇岭脚村区域动工建设吉达港。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月开始，当地政府强行封锁岭脚村前海修建电煤码头，致使长期以捕鱼为生的村民收入骤减。本来当地政府承诺给村民每户</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span><span>万元补偿，后来竟然被克扣到每户</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>百元。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span>前些日子，村里组织多位村民集体到省里上访，没有结果。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2013</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">16</span><span>日，岭脚村大量村民在前海抗议政府征地封海，遭上千警察镇压，包括老人小孩在内的多名村民被打伤。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-CLpH52v68PA/UjfTFwhrGxI/AAAAAAAAoRo/Wa1IBzT7onI/s1600/1.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"400\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-CLpH52v68PA/UjfTFwhrGxI/AAAAAAAAoRo/Wa1IBzT7onI/s400/1.JPG\" width=\"301\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-f8ulp9WWj9I/UjfTHW3-3nI/AAAAAAAAoRw/aO3jblGX8Wk/s1600/2.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"296\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-f8ulp9WWj9I/UjfTHW3-3nI/AAAAAAAAoRw/aO3jblGX8Wk/s400/2.jpg\" width=\"400\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-fFO-OS-YSV4/UjfTIipaynI/AAAAAAAAoR4/1m_r5s8EOdg/s1600/3.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"400\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-fFO-OS-YSV4/UjfTIipaynI/AAAAAAAAoR4/1m_r5s8EOdg/s400/3.jpg\" width=\"290\" /></a></div>\n<p> </div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://